'''Equipment''' in Dragon Warrior III includes weapons, armor, shields, and helmets. Equipment availability depends on character class.

== Equipment by Class ==

=== Hero ===
* Most weapons
* Most armor
* All shields
* All helmets

=== Soldier ===
* Heavy weapons (swords, axes)
* Heavy armor
* All shields
* All helmets

=== Pilgrim ===
* Maces, staffs
* Medium armor
* Some shields
* Medium helmets

=== Wizard ===
* Staffs, daggers
* Robes
* No shields
* Light helmets

=== Fighter ===
* Claws, chain weapons
* Light armor
* Limited shields
* Light helmets

=== Merchant ===
* Various weapons
* Medium armor
* Most shields
* Medium helmets

=== Goof-off ===
* Random equipment
* Limited options
* Some unique items

