== Equipment Tips ==

'''Hero:'''
* Can use almost everything
* Ultimate equipment makes strongest character
* Sword of Kings is worth finding

'''Soldier:'''
* Heavy armor focus
* Best shield users
* Axes for high damage

'''Fighter:'''
* Claws are class-specific
* Light armor limits defense
* High agility compensates

'''Wizard/Sage:'''
* Staff of Thunder is excellent
* Defense is secondary to magic
* Magical Robe for protection

'''Class Changes:'''
* Equipment may need swapping after class change
* Plan equipment before changing
* Some items can't be re-equipped

== Cursed Equipment ==

Beware of cursed items:
* Cannot be unequipped normally
* Visit church to remove
* Usually high stats as compensation

